{
  "id": "RAW_69461f",
  "title": "Step-R1-V-Mini 发布：多模态推理新成员，轻量亦强大",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/84-m-C_AW4e5B21vLml_pw",
  "date": "2025-04-08 12:17:08",
  "author": "阶跃星辰",
  "siteName": "阶跃星辰",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">此前我们先后推出视觉理解模型 Step-1V、Step-1.5V，以及语言推理模型 Step-R-mini。</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，阶跃星辰正式发布全新</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 91, 219);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">多模态推理模型——Step-R1-V-Mini</span></span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，支持图文输入、文字输出、有良好的指令遵循和通用能力，能够</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">高精度感知图像并完成复杂推理任务</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-R1-V-Mini 已正式上线阶跃AI 网页端，并在阶跃星辰开放平台提供 API 接口，欢迎体验：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">阶跃AI 网页端：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><br></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">https://yuewen.cn/chats/new</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">阶跃星辰开放平台：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 8px 8px 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 8px 8px 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">https://platform.stepfun.com/docs/llm/reasoning</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6c2cfed-153b-44e1-329f-b368a44f8600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7893738140417458\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1054\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001701\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6c2cfed-153b-44e1-329f-b368a44f8600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">阶跃AI 网页端已上线</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">技术亮点</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了提升模型在多模态协同场景下的推理表现，我们在训练方法上做了两项重要尝试：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第一，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">多模态</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">联合强化学习</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-R1-V-Mini 的训练路径基于 PPO 强化学习策略，在图像空间引入 verifiable reward 来解决图片空间推理链路复杂、容易产生混淆的相关和因果推理错误的问题。相较 DPO 等方法，在处理图像空间的复杂链路时更具泛化性与鲁棒性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第二，充分利用多模态合成数据</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前多模态数据的反馈信号相对难以获得。我们设计了大量基于环境反馈的多模态数据合成链路，合成了可规模化训练的多模态推理数据，并通过基于 PPO 的强化学习训练同步提升模型文本和视觉的推理能力，有效避免了训练跷跷板问题。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">视觉推理榜单成绩领先</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-R1-V-Mini</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;在多个公开榜单中表现亮眼，在&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">MathVision</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;视觉推理榜单位列国内第一，在视觉推理、数学逻辑和代码等方面表现优异。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0LDJQiaWfxznjPDQL2574L9XMvM7ekibchv8jR1yAynm66zCyhn0CBibCmwicVoGdbe6yxictqoQwzfCdUic7s5icSudQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"100001674\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc8ebf70-adc4-4427-af1b-84184820ac00/public\" style=\"width: 100%; pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc8ebf70-adc4-4427-af1b-84184820ac00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">案例分享</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <h4 style=\"text-align: left;margin: 24px 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">案例1：看图识地点</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">输入网友温布利球场的实拍图片，Step-R1-V-Mini 能迅速识别图中元素进行地点推理，结合图中的不同元素，如颜色、物体（体育场、曼城队徽）等等，综合后做出判断，得出温布利体育场，并给出对战双方的可能。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n   <section style=\"will-change: transform;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;height: auto;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden auto;scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;\">\n      <section style=\"height: 0px;padding-top: 0.02px;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;\">\n        <section style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n         <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b863982-2a93-478c-3a03-07c1648ec200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"3.4865771812080535\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"894\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;width:100%;visibility:visible !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0LDJQiaWfxznjPDQL2574L9XMvM7ekibchtv0UicLFibacYYu9yIVZqVyKsLcTFsFwP7CFseDibZ4fC7CusHG7IP86Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"556\" data-cropsely2=\"1999\" data-imgfileid=\"100001682\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b863982-2a93-478c-3a03-07c1648ec200/public\">\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"height: 0px;padding-top: 100%;\">\n       <svg viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;text-indent: 0em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和当时的比赛资料核对后，</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-R1-V-Mini 推理的很准确。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/55514365-7510-43a2-8b50-65c068c73700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1536050156739812\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"638\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"638\" data-height=\"98\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"86\" data-imgfileid=\"100001651\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/55514365-7510-43a2-8b50-65c068c73700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">案例2：看图识菜谱</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">输入一张美食图，无论是菜品还是蘸料，统统识别得清清楚楚，并把做法详细到</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;text-decoration: none;\">“鲜虾 300g、大葱白2根”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">等具体用量，识别精准推理严谨。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n   <section style=\"will-change: transform;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;height: auto;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden auto;scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;\">\n      <section style=\"height: 0px;padding-top: 0.02px;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;\">\n        <section style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n         <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0LDJQiaWfxznjPDQL2574L9XMvM7ekibchHpj1gejcHD8NTjdN4Zo9OKroWf03M7iaico8jJ1JrMy5A8o6E19Vyp1Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"556\" data-cropsely2=\"1999\" data-imgfileid=\"100001681\" data-ratio=\"6.95067264573991\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/32646556-8aea-41d3-aaf1-de302a545900/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"892\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;width:100%;visibility:visible !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/32646556-8aea-41d3-aaf1-de302a545900/public\">\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"height: 0px;padding-top: 100%;\">\n       <svg viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;text-indent: 0em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">案例3：物体数量计算</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">输入一张含有不同形状、不同颜色、不同位置的物体摆放图，从空间感知、颜色形状、逻辑推理逐一识别，根据物体的颜色、形状、位置推理计算，最终得出剩下的物体数量是 8-1 =7。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n   <section style=\"will-change: transform;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;height: auto;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden auto;scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;\">\n      <section style=\"height: 0px;padding-top: 0.02px;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;\">\n        <section style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n         <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b8ca5ed2-3017-4f26-2542-815efccc6e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"6.709821428571429\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"896\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;width:100%;visibility:visible !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0LDJQiaWfxznjPDQL2574L9XMvM7ekibchlkJSXicv4k5ibM0VOkXvvaKtoiahZnEOiaNU2neI3I7kWm8e2MibY30K86w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"556\" data-cropsely2=\"4033\" data-imgfileid=\"100001683\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b8ca5ed2-3017-4f26-2542-815efccc6e00/public\">\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"height: 0px;padding-top: 100%;\">\n       <svg viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-indent: 0em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-R1-V-Mini 是我们在多模态推理方向的阶段性成果，欢迎大家体验并反馈。我们也将在推理模型方向持续探索，敬请期待。</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 40px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">推荐阅读</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTYxNzg5Mg==&amp;mid=2247484738&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=aa4f2f4363f93387ea6696e4cc87ee81&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0LDJQiaWfxznjPDQL2574L9XMvM7ekibchNYWcFNY8WlSiacb9L0hgtWTy2sz9aoTUBicFu6vgia8HTKyPEyPOT8fOQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span style=\"width:100%;\" class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/01831cbc-f485-4e21-724d-02fb671ed000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0LDJQiaWfxznjPDQL2574L9XMvM7ekibchNYWcFNY8WlSiacb9L0hgtWTy2sz9aoTUBicFu6vgia8HTKyPEyPOT8fOQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"100001670\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/01831cbc-f485-4e21-724d-02fb671ed000/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阶跃星辰发布多模态推理模型 Step-R1-V-Mini，支持图文输入和文字输出，擅长高精度图像感知和复杂推理任务，并在 MathVision 等多个视觉推理榜单上名列前茅。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阶跃星辰发布多模态推理模型 Step-R1-V-Mini，支持图文输入和文字输出，擅长高精度图像感知和复杂推理任务，并在 MathVision 等多个视觉推理榜单上名列前茅。",
  "summary": "阶跃星辰发布了全新的多模态推理模型 Step-R1-V-Mini，该模型支持图文输入和文字输出，具备良好的指令遵循和通用能力，尤其擅长高精度感知图像并完成复杂推理任务，例如图像识别、菜谱识别、物体数量计算等。该模型基于多模态联合强化学习和多模态合成数据进行训练，在 MathVision 等多个视觉推理榜单中表现出色。Step-R1-V-Mini 已在阶跃 AI 网页端和阶跃星辰开放平台提供服务。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "多模态联合强化学习提升推理表现",
      "explanation": "Step-R1-V-Mini 基于 PPO 强化学习策略，引入 verifiable reward 解决图片空间推理问题，具有更好的泛化性和鲁棒性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "多模态合成数据有效提升模型能力",
      "explanation": "通过设计基于环境反馈的多模态数据合成链路，规模化训练模型，同步提升文本和视觉的推理能力，避免训练跷跷板问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Step-R1-V-Mini 在视觉推理榜单成绩领先",
      "explanation": "在 MathVision 视觉推理榜单位列国内第一，在视觉推理、数学逻辑和代码等方面表现优异。"
    }
  ],
